_sText:
I'm a Chinese mapper, and this is my first map (I really like JB game mode), designed in a Minecraft style. Since it's my first map, I might not have managed the size well, so it's quite huge. I've almost reached Hammer's limits. If you find any bugs, please let me know. Have fun! (The map includes some Chinese elements, but they won't interfere with your gameplay)

----Game----
Soccer
GlassFight x2
Car
PacMan
BomberMan
VolleyBall
Climb
LongJump
Drop
DodgeBall
SimonSay
Range
BreakFloor
4Color
HotPotato
JumpRope
Pool
BasketBall

And some Secrets

If you have any suggestions for my current map, please let me know. Thank you! I might start working on another JB map or an MG map next.
Most of the map's architectural design is inspired by KanaCraft.
